  "title": "Two people reported a star-like UFO over Juvevê-PR [1990]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/08/two-people-reported-a-star-like-ufo-over-juveve-pr-1990/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1x4",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 24th, 1990</strong>. Time: 6:30 pm. Duration: 3 minutes. Two people in the region of Juvevê, Curitiba, State of Paraná, spotted an unidentified flying object &#8220;passing over the building&#8221; [where the two witnesses were] about 10km high. According to the witnesses, the UFO had the &#8220;shape of a star&#8221;, but &#8220;bigger&#8221;, and had the &#8220;silver color&#8221;. The sighting was carried out with the naked eye and with good visibility conditions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.285. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado próximo à Praia de Juvevê, Curitiba, Paraná</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
